the multiplayer aspect and also the emotional aspect.

52
00:02:28,374 --> 00:02:29,696
We want to get both of these right.

53
00:02:31,278 --> 00:02:35,021
I think we're in the home stretch now, we're nearly finished with the game and ready to

54
