kind of launch the global release.

55
00:02:37,583 --> 00:02:42,707
But I'm so passionate about this area that I feel that over the past decade, emotional

56
00:02:42,747 --> 00:02:49,452
storytelling has really seen some highlights over the past few years, primarily in the

57
00:02:49,552 --> 00:02:51,214
linear game experience.

58
00:02:51,754 --> 00:02:56,938
And what I hope today will do is to offer additional conversation to explore emotional

59
00:02:56,978 --> 00:03:00,241
storytelling in the multiplayer domain as well.

60
00:03:02,399 --> 00:03:04,961
So I would say that Sky is a spiritual successor

61
00:03:04,981 --> 00:03:07,563
to some of the previous games that the studio have made.

62
00:03:08,804 --> 00:03:10,305
I studied screenwriting at school,

63
