but boy, this studio does things very, very differently.

64
00:03:15,069 --> 00:03:16,390
But they did break from tradition

65
00:03:16,510 --> 00:03:17,871
compared to their previous games.

66
00:03:18,251 --> 00:03:21,494
So Sky is the first fully-fledged multiplayer experience

67
00:03:21,514 --> 00:03:22,234
that they've launched.

68
00:03:22,254 --> 00:03:24,977
It's gonna be multi-format, coming on iOS first.

69
00:03:25,817 --> 00:03:27,619
